just like (snaps fingers).

64
00:06:00,365 --> 00:06:01,906
- Joseph has excelled in his studies.

65
00:06:01,906 --> 00:06:03,223
He's demonstrated his readiness.

66
00:06:03,223 --> 00:06:06,534
He begins by helping Ashton and

