00:33:11,259 --> 00:33:13,613
- I've done it before.

565
00:33:13,613 --> 00:33:14,613
- All right.

566
00:33:16,434 --> 00:33:17,267
We'll see.

567
00:33:21,778 --> 00:33:24,095
This is where you'll work.

568
00:33:24,095 --> 00:33:26,095
However, any phone calls

569
00:33:28,315 --> 00:33:30,047
will be made by me.

570
00:33:30,047 --> 00:33:33,175
There'll be no attempt
at outside communication.

571
00:33:33,175 --> 00:33:35,109
Let me be clear on this.

572
00:33:35,109 --> 00:33:39,276
My back's against the wall,
and that's given you a chance.

573
00:33:40,275 --> 00:33:44,112
Abuse it, and you'll live
just long enough to regret it.

574
00:33:44,112 --> 00:33:45,204
- I understand.

575
00:33:45,204 --> 00:33:47,670
- Let me add a last word of caution.

576
00:33:47,670 --> 00:33:51,165
You may understandably care
nothing for your brothers,

577
00:33:51,165 --> 00:33:52,719
but I'm sure you wish no harm

578
00:33:52,719 --> 00:33:55,552
