at the mercy of the market.

626
00:36:36,437 --> 00:36:37,941
Supply and demand.

627
00:36:37,941 --> 00:36:40,496
If I were you, I'd create my own demand.

628
00:36:40,496 --> 00:36:41,761
- How so?

629
00:36:41,761 --> 00:36:44,482
- Well, do some homework
on some current trends.

630
00:36:44,482 --> 00:36:48,733
Then move towards design
and manufacturing.

631
00:36:48,733 --> 00:36:49,767
You've already got the labor,

632
00:36:49,767 --> 00:36:53,021
maybe even some untapped
talent if you check, you know.

633
00:36:53,021 --> 00:36:55,372
- No, there's no way I can risk

634
00:36:55,372 --> 00:36:57,214
calling attention to my business here.

635
00:36:57,214 --> 00:36:59,378
- Oh, of course, of course.

636
00:36:59,378 --> 00:37:01,502
And that's why, that's why

637
00:37:01,502 --> 00:37:04,777
you set up a legitimate arm
of business out of state.

638
00:37:04,777 --> 00:37:08,093
You know, kind of like a
front or something, you know.

639
00:37:08,093 --> 00:37:11,676
Then you funnel your
products through that.

640
00:37:13,740 --> 00:37:16,657
- And why would David help Goliath?

641
00:37:21,164 --> 00:37:22,081
- A chance.

642
00:37:25,043 --> 00:37:25,876
- Hi.

643
00:37:25,876 --> 00:37:26,709
- [Woman] Hi.

