00:37:26,709 --> 00:37:29,151
- Remember the designs we talked about?

645
00:37:29,151 --> 00:37:31,729
Did you think of a few.

646
00:37:31,729 --> 00:37:33,705
Remember the designs we talked about?

647
00:37:33,705 --> 00:37:35,301
No, no?

648
00:37:35,301 --> 00:37:37,552
Remember the designs we
talked about earlier?

649
00:37:37,552 --> 00:37:40,118
You think you can maybe write a few down?

650
00:37:40,118 --> 00:37:40,951
No.

651
00:37:41,982 --> 00:37:43,457
- Hi, Emily.

652
00:37:43,457 --> 00:37:46,996
Hi, remember the designs
we talked about earlier?

653
00:37:46,996 --> 00:37:48,400
- Hello, Martha.

654
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:49,819
How are you?

655
00:37:49,819 --> 00:37:52,326
Well, I came by to drop off a pad.

656
00:37:52,326 --> 00:37:53,979
I know you had a few designs

657
00:37:53,979 --> 00:37:57,545
you wanted to write down for me, right?

658
00:37:57,545 --> 00:37:58,378
Right?

659
00:37:59,223 --> 00:38:00,056
Right?

660
00:38:02,282 --> 00:38:03,789
Well, I'll tell you what.

661
00:38:03,789 --> 00:38:04,622
I'll.

662
00:38:12,678 --> 00:38:14,100
Bye, Martha.

