00:39:23,625 --> 00:39:27,338
But don't worry, Diane's
taking care of him.

674
00:39:27,338 --> 00:39:29,250
Just the way you took care of her

675
00:39:29,250 --> 00:39:31,500
when she was a little girl.

676
00:39:33,389 --> 00:39:35,472
- Can I get you anything?

677
00:39:39,026 --> 00:39:40,693
I miss Mama so much.

678
00:39:42,544 --> 00:39:43,377
- So do I.

679
00:39:57,630 --> 00:40:00,547
(machines running)

680
00:40:03,254 --> 00:40:06,122
- Thank you, thank you,
these are great, thank you.

681
00:40:06,122 --> 00:40:07,167
Hi, Emily.

682
00:40:07,167 --> 00:40:09,745
- Hi, I've got the designs for you.

683
00:40:09,745 --> 00:40:11,008
Do you like them?

684
00:40:11,008 --> 00:40:12,682
- Ho ho, do I like these?

685
00:40:12,682 --> 00:40:14,232
Mr. Childress is gonna love these.

686
00:40:14,232 --> 00:40:17,399
Thank you very much, Emily, thank you.

687
00:40:18,475 --> 00:40:19,392
Hi, Martha.

688
00:40:20,929 --> 00:40:22,429
Hello, I was just.

689
00:40:24,673 --> 00:40:25,506
Oh, wow.

690
00:40:29,005 --> 00:40:29,838
Wow.

691
00:40:31,455 --> 00:40:35,269
Martha, these are, these are fantastic.

692
00:40:35,269 --> 00:40:38,352
Thank you, thank you very much.

