00:42:45,074 --> 00:42:48,357
Clara decided it was
finally time to take a look.

741
00:42:48,357 --> 00:42:50,955
- Mrs. Childress, how are you?

742
00:42:50,955 --> 00:42:52,295
Pleasure to meet you.

743
00:42:52,295 --> 00:42:55,546
- Joe, or do you prefer Joseph?

744
00:42:55,546 --> 00:42:57,593
- Joe is fine, it doesn't matter.

745
00:42:57,593 --> 00:43:01,259
- I must say, you're not
at all what I expected.

746
00:43:01,259 --> 00:43:04,974
All these improvements,
they're your ideas?

747
00:43:04,974 --> 00:43:09,035
- Well, let's call it
a cooperative effort.

748
00:43:09,035 --> 00:43:11,003
- With Frank out of town
so much more these days,

749
00:43:11,003 --> 00:43:13,400
I decided to check out the competition.

750
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:15,131
I'm impressed.

751
00:43:15,131 --> 00:43:18,290
