our more successful fashions.

752
00:43:18,290 --> 00:43:20,856
She has a great sense of design.

753
00:43:20,856 --> 00:43:23,794
She was a model, you know.

754
00:43:23,794 --> 00:43:26,133
- Well, I wish I could stay longer,

755
00:43:26,133 --> 00:43:29,283
but my afternoon's completely booked, so.

756
00:43:29,283 --> 00:43:30,532
- [Childress] Well then,
let's finish the tour

757
00:43:30,532 --> 00:43:31,868
