758
00:43:31,868 --> 00:43:33,139
- I was a pleasure to meet you, Joe.

759
00:43:33,139 --> 00:43:35,844
- [Joseph] Pleasure to
meet you, Mrs. Childress.

760
00:43:35,844 --> 00:43:38,344
- I'm sure I'll see you again.

761
00:43:51,356 --> 00:43:54,189
