she has some great ideas.

772
00:44:26,256 --> 00:44:27,923
She'll surprise you.

773
00:44:29,464 --> 00:44:32,851
Fill me in when I get back this afternoon.

774
00:44:32,851 --> 00:44:33,768
- Yes, sir.

775
00:44:43,035 --> 00:44:47,040
- I have a confession
to make, so they say.

776
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,019
I knew about Frank's appointment.

777
00:44:49,019 --> 00:44:50,889
I wanted to speak to you alone.

778
00:44:50,889 --> 00:44:51,722
- Oh?

779
00:44:54,552 --> 00:44:58,221
- I wanted to thank you for
everything you've done here.

780
00:44:58,221 --> 00:45:00,404
