♪ My brothers left me high and dry ♪

1571
01:32:53,584 --> 01:32:58,584
♪ Did you believe their lies? ♪

1572
01:32:59,627 --> 01:33:04,627
♪ For so long I've been restless ♪

1573
01:33:05,902 --> 01:33:10,627
♪ All I want is forgiveness ♪

